verbose_text: At the system level when all crops were grown under ZT with full CA practices in Scenarios 3 and 4, T & CE costs decreased by INR 9900-10350 ha -1 compared to PTR, whereas this reduction was INR 4500 ha -1 in Scenario 2 in which partial CA was practiced.
